  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Guidance for parents and carers of children attending out-of-school settings during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for parents and carers of children attending community activities, holiday or after-school clubs, tuition and other out-of-school settings.</p>

  </div>
</div>

